DESCRIPTION

- A little game I made in 3 weeks or so.  Also, my first game ever so expect a few bugs in audio and maybe in other things.  👾

- A game made just with squares in which you will have to pass 13 levels dodging enemies and doing it as fast as posible while listening to the epic music.  💀

- I know it's hard just keep trying. Also tell me anything which I could make better or ideas to improve/add content to the game. 🔥
